gomodel:SYNGO_854  a      owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Pre-embedding immunoperoxidase and immunogold electron microscopy VAChT immunoreactivity in presynaptic terminals (Fig. 4c,d,e) and on synaptic vesicles (Fig. 4f,g,h), respectively.\n\nA rabbit polyclonal antibody directed against the C-terminus of VAChT was generated in the study. The specificity of the antibody was tested by Western Blotting (Fig. 1) and immunohistochemistry (Fig. 3 a,b). No KO-control.. Experimental description: Adult male Sprague-Dawley rats (n = 8) were given 300 IU of heparin i.p., deeply anesthetized with ..." , "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0030285 replaced by GO:0030672" ;
